# --- 楂樺痉鍦板浘閰嶇疆 (鍓嶇鍙锛涜鍦ㄩ珮寰锋帶鍒跺彴鍋氬煙鍚嶇櫧鍚嶅崟/閰嶉鎺у埗) ---
# 鐢宠鍦板潃锛歨ttps://console.amap.com/dev/key/app
VITE_APP_AMAP_KEY=__AMAP_KEY__
VITE_APP_AMAP_SECURITY_CODE=__AMAP_SECURITY_CODE__

# --- 鍚庣鎺ュ彛閰嶇疆 ---
# 缁熶竴鍓嶇紑绛栫暐锛氬墠绔姹備娇鐢?/api/v1/...
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api/v1

# --- 搴旂敤鐜 ---
VITE_APP_ENV=development

# Backend target used by vite dev proxy
VITE_BACKEND_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:8000
